Package algorithms.bipartite

Class FlowNetwork

java.lang.Object
algorithms.bipartite.FlowNetwork
public class FlowNetwork extends Object
class representing a flow network for MinCostUnbalancedAssignment.java If the sink and source nodes and weights are set in the origin graph, sink and source logic is used in code.
Author:
nichole
